/alerts/*      → proxy to incident-service (already same service)
/audit-logs/*  → proxy to audit-service :4003
/policy-logs/* → proxy to audit-service :4003
/policies/*    → proxy to firewall-service (via existing /firewall proxy, or new mount)
```

